Thank you for using the Overstock shopping app! This update includes the following features:

- Personalized home screen.
- Voice search support.

Every update includes stability and performance improvements as well.

If you have any questions or experience any issue please contact us at iosfeedback@overstock.com

Thank you for using the Overstock shopping app! This update includes the following feature:
- minor bug fixes.
Every update includes stability and performance improvements as well.

Overstock now includes an augmented reality (AR) feature which lets our customers visualize thousands of top products in their room next to their own furniture to see how the size, textures, and colors match their current room’s design and flow.

With the new AR feature you can:
+ Visualize a product within your room and see coordinating items to design and build your dream room
+ Save and share pictures of your new design to your photo library and text or share with your friends and family on your favorite social network
+ Add products to your cart or purchase using Apple Pay via Touch ID without leaving the AR screen

Thank you for using the Overstock shopping app!
+ Check out our new look and fun improvements to bring you the best deals for the holidays.

Every update includes stability and performance improvements as well.

Santa is coming!!! We’ve worked on some improvements to provide even better gift ideas and deals that end up on Santa’s sleigh.

In case you forgot we’ve got some fantastic ideas to make up for a late Christmas!

Santa has come and gone, so we decided to clean up the wrapping paper and the bugs he left behind.

We learned from Santa that checking your lists is important, so we’ve improved our favorite and list features in the app.
